Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,== Dialogue ============================

Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he had had that talk with NK,\Nthings seem kind of tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he had had that talk with NK,\Nthings seem kind of tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Not looking good.\N--It's gone to ruin, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is toxic gas from the harmful bacteria\Nthat live in the intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--"Toxic gas"?\N--"Toxic gas"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, his friends are all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There are up to a hundred trillion\Nbacteria in the intestines, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we're sure to find them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't sound the least bit relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you two, I don't care what\Nyou do as long as you're quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to know we're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I've fought with him once in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to use that experience today\Nto head to the front lines as a Memory T Cell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and finish off the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I just have a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this guy you keep mentioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--A Cancer Cell.\N--A Cancer Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cancer Cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Platelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Watch out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's meeting us head-on this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really came back to life just so you could\Nthrow a tantrum, you stupid Cancer Cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you fell for it! He's nothing but a puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the effort you had\Nto put in against a mere doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you've gotten\Nyourselves into, Immune Cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the trio from before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancer Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This just might be what they call fate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For the three of you from that day\Nto saunter right toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, which of us, me or you three,\Nis on the side of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle it once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,NK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a one-trick pony\Nwhen it comes to attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us, NK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You can gloat after you've untied us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... Boy, would you mind\Ntelling me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come back to life\Nwhen you knew you'd only be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you actually thought\Nyou could win this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my second time battling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tactics are a little too exposed for you\Nto be picking a fight with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to pick a fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I've found\Nwhat it is I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted you three to bear witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised? These are all the same\Nas that puppet you just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all fragments of my tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stab them with your sword,\Nbut they won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll keep moving forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a thing that you can do.\NJust resign yourselves to being my captives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you, NK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Over by you, too, Neutrophil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Memory T Cell, and I've seen\Nevery one of your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory T Cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning you're not quite\Nthe same guy you were before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I can foresee your every next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindly cease your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are not the appropriate responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not an enemy from the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born of this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a cell just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow any attacks on the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Regulatory T Cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulatory T Cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They control the activity of T Cells to prevent\Nthem from triggering anomalous immune responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No good! Memory T!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Neutrophil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...146, where are you? Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,1146! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, 1146! Come in--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd protect him.\NI was sure you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a nice, long chat...\Ninstead of killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu! Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those germs still behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep our handkerchiefs pressed\Nto our mouths and run low to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the intestine is in\Neven worse shape than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Red Blood Cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you see... I don't think\Nwe can take this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The bacteria's invaded the area up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Take another route and run as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Red Blood Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be fine, Backward Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Platelets seem really anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be their rock now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, we're going to run\Nat top speed, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,NK! Memory T!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancer Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory T!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here, Cancer Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't I the one you wanted to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a grudge against me,\Nthen I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do, White Blood Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't fly off the handle\Nwhen you're all banged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to value your own life more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you agree to what I'm about to say,\NI'll let you out of there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm sure it's tearing you apart\Nto be locked up and helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulatory T Cell, open this door, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll kill this\NCancer Cell! So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill? I can't open that door\Nif you're going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As he's in no way an external enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulatory T Cell's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulatory T Cells are responsible\Nfor reining in the activity of Immune Cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,preventing them from attacking the body's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,own tissues or cells that\Nare beneficial to the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, as the Cancer Cell\Noriginated from this body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of recognizing him as\Na foreign substance, a non-self cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,she is trying to suppress\Nthe Immune Cells' attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she's betraying you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that lady's job, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancer Cell, I'm gonna kill--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...ever attack other cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You normal cells are all so dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, despite being dead serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,White Blood Cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...you rescued that ordinary cell\Nand those Lactic Acid Bacteria, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,About that... The only reason I didn't kill them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was because those bacteria\Nweren't toxic to this body! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I get that, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is, I've changed my mind\Nsomewhat. It got me thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lives that are necessary\Nand lives that are not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does such a distinction\Nhave to made at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's so tragic for us to be taking lives\Nor being robbed of our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,why do we have to keep repeating\Nthat cycle over and over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\NHave you ever had a thought like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the sake of this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's necessary!\NThat's why we die and kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then let's take it a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives of trillions of cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or this body's one life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We cells are killed, burn with hatred\Nfor each other and are sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all so that this body can go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of us who get killed, and you guys,\Nthe ones who kill... We've all suffered so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how about a world where we cells\Ndon't have to kill or be killed at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a world gone mad,\Napproaching death...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's to make that world a reality\Neven for a split second...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't you think we'd be justified\Nin sacrificing the life of this body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you! No way will\NI ever let you do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here, Cancer Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! You're horrendously wrong,\Nbut I'll set you straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If this body dies, that means that\Nall of us cells will die with it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, we'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll die after we've been liberated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's my job to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong about that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could pull that off--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulatory T Cell is siding with me.\NNot to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...this place, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Those fumes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...harmful bacteria...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...toxins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When the new world is completed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...then let's be friends, all right,\NWhite Blood Cell, you kindhearted assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Cancer Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,NK! Memory T! Regulatory T Cell!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're more worried\Nabout your friends than yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's what I like about you\Nalong with all the contradictions you bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you can only live\Nfor someone else's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you were born a cell who can\Ndo nothing but kill others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching you, I feel such pity and impatience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's so entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of all your yammering,\Nyou annoying little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancer Cell, I'm gonna kill--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...ever attack other cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize you've been repeating\Nthe same conversation over and over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--What are you, a moron?\N--Sh-Shut the cell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As if... I had time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...to think... of different lines...\Nevery single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...is that the only move you've got,\Npounding him head-on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you at least try a different\Nmove for once, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! This is how I've always been, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tactics were never your strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Easily swayed by your emotions,\Nunable to thrive on victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and unable to use defeat as a stepping-stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never be able to defeat me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile to even struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it go and cease your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're surrounded! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lactic acid bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bacteria that work to support\Nthe health of the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a variety of features.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Lactic Acid Bacterium!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll p-protect--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! This cell just said he's going\Nto protect that lactic acid bacterium!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty funny, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmful bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathogenic E. coli, Staphylococci,\NClostridium and the like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,cause proteins to degrade\Nand produce toxic by-products.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we test you to see\Nif you can really protect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can withstand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Harmful Bacteria Toxic Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The toxicity of harmful bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Toxic effects of harmful bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,include intestinal putrefaction,\Nproduction of toxins and carcinogens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A host of deleterious effects to the human body\Ncan ensue, such as a weakened immune system,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,foul-smelling stools and gas,\Nand diarrhea or constipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--My legs!\N--Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us a good time, Cell boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We came all this way to this side\Nof the intestinal wall
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,only to find it duller than we thought,\Nso it's been a real gut punch for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to torment you every which way,\Nso be sure to show us some juicy reactions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu! Nyu-nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a lame attack is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lactic Acid Bacterium!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! You miserable good bacteria runt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a germ,\Nand yet you're sucking up to a cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you dare turn on us,\NI'll obliterate you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu! Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away, Lactic Acid Bacterium!\NJust run away as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!\NJust run and save yourself! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu! Nyuuu! Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy! Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here now! I said go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Now that was one lame farce\Nyou made us watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that you were the only one\Nwho got such a sad goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right. As long as you can\Ngo on living, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up to be a strong,\Nfine lactic acid bacterium, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for us to have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It seems like you've really got\Nyour hands full, White Blood Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our battle has hardly even begun yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our battle has hardly even begun yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our battle has hardly even begun yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode of {\i1}Cells at Work!!{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Target sighted!
